title: Jose Blanco - Cuenca Y Blanco Cigars
itunes:title: Jose Blanco - Cuenca Y Blanco Cigars
description: We're smoking 3 cigars and talking sports with NBC Radio's Anthony Pepe from "The Bawstin Diehards." We light up Anthony's cigar, Bert Sugar, name after the great boxing sports writer. We  bring on Jose Blanco, the "B" in "CyB Cigars" and talk about the Cigar Symposium. Last but not least, we review the contender's for The Cigar of The Year before the Big Announcement!
